A Java AOP timer for classes that are annotated with @Service. Shows how long the execution of a method took in milliseconds.

It utilizes Spring profiles. The profiling aspect is turned on only for the Spring profile named "diagnostic". This is achieved via command line options.

To turn on profiling in pom.xml uncomment this line:
<argument>-Dspring.profiles.active=diagnostic</argument>

build with: mvn clean install
run with: mvn exec:exec